<p><code class="language-plaintext success highlighter-rouge">æ­£ç¡®ï¼šåŒæ—¶æ›´æ–°</code>
\(temp0:=\theta_{0}-\alpha\frac{\partial}{\partial\theta_{0}}J(\theta_{0},\theta_{1}) \\
